153	//     as JSON, or that parses but is not a recognised EvidenceBundle/`{bundles:[...]}` shape
154	// The ONE case that stays a silent skip: a file discovered while walking a MIXED DIRECTORY (gate-cli
155	// hands this gate the shared eval/calibration-known-bad/fixtures/ directory, which legitimately
156	// holds fixtures belonging to every other gate too) that is not this gate's shape - that is
157	// recognised, not swallowed, exactly like catalogue/linters/lib.js's own "not a rule/record" case.
